{"tid":2280281,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"台片《怪胎》疑抄襲港片《寵我》被入稟告侵權兼禁上映","createTime":"2020-11-10T11:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T11:48:11.000Z","uid":346775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6730a283ac597a1ec5bbc6e7440cd87993a42bf0","tid":2280281,"uid":346775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"浪漫喜劇電影《怪胎》在台灣票房大賣，本月將於香港上映。有電影製作公司昨入稟高等法院，指《怪胎》抄襲其電影《寵我》的主要情節，包括男女主角患有強迫症、須戴口罩、穿上雨衣和手套等。該電影製作公司要求高院頒令，禁止《怪胎》侵犯版權或在香港上映等。<br />\n<br />\n原告為電影公司JK Holdings Limited，被告依次為牽猴子整合行銷股份有限公司、滿滿額娛樂股份有限公司以及台灣導演廖明毅。根據入禀狀，首被告及次被告為台灣電影《怪胎》的製作公司，第三被告為該電影的編劇及導演。原告曾於2017年出品其首部電影《寵我》，該電影曾獲得149個電影獎項。原告指控《怪胎》抄襲《寵我》的主要元素，包括以男女主角身穿雨衣、手套、戴上口罩等畫面，呈現強迫症議題，以及運用特定顏色組合。入稟狀又指，被告曾作出虛假陳述，誤導公眾指《怪胎》是授權改編自《寵我》。<br />\n<br />\n《怪胎》將於本月19日在香港上映。被告透過各大社交平台及電影大堂等宣傳電影，導致原告蒙受損失。原告要求法庭禁止被告侵犯其版權、以及用電影《怪胎》謀利，包括禁止於香港上映以及售賣相關產品。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA1896/20】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/7XQFCAKIAFBL5PGQKI7F76LQLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2F7XQFCAKIAFBL5PGQKI7F76LQLM%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ikx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=a2e7001f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2F7XQFCAKIAFBL5PGQKI7F76LQLM%2F&h=04de7219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/7XQFCAKIAFBL5PGQKI7F76LQLM/</a>"},{"pid":"f488cc3cb2d47b24c63d2034e183feb6ba56d43a","tid":2280281,"uid":346775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"台灣《怪胎》有回應：<br />\n針對香港出現的告訴，《怪胎》監製陳怡樺再次強調本片是編導廖明毅的原創作品，沒有抄襲，且先前收到對方的律師信後，也已請律師正式回函否認並澄清沒有抄襲一事。在台灣，對方也並無提告。至於對方反而告到香港？監製表示「匪夷所思」，已聯絡香港律師進行後續處理，但香港11月19日上映行程不會改變，因為《怪胎》並無抄襲一事。<br />\n<br />\n針對抄襲指控，《怪胎》監製陳怡樺9月曾回應：「莫名其妙！那部片我們連聽都沒聽過，更別說看過，也完全不清楚那部片在描述什麼。」強調《怪胎》的故事發想完全是編導廖明毅個人自我創作，並已回覆律師信。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/PDMJWNU235FGBGVT6KJ4P6Y7EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2FPDMJWNU235FGBGVT6KJ4P6Y7EA%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ikx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=97b9b68b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2FPDMJWNU235FGBGVT6KJ4P6Y7EA%2F&h=48238905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/PDMJWNU235FGBGVT6KJ4P6Y7EA/</a>"},{"pid":"19df1fed4057ddad7665b47fb6c24808124bbbfb","tid":2280281,"uid":346775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"附上兩套戲預告片對比<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gyEy8rjt0qc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgyEy8rjt0qc&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ikx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=c726c872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gyEy8rjt0qc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=byDWAoKEFZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbyDWAoKEFZ8&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ikx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=28c0c639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=byDWAoKEFZ8</a><br />\n<br />\n真係睇唔出邊度抄襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都夠膽告"},{"pid":"dbad8630ab192280803680544fe2a987c1af97a6","tid":2280281,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"套寵我jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}